                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9744" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1467</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">698 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">国资旗舰深投控：使命为帆，能否引领怡亚通破浪前行？</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Being the flagship of SOEs, with mission as the sail, can Shenzhen Investment Holdings guide Eternal Asia to navigate through the waves?</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">陈玉罡，卢珊</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中山大学管理学院</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">深圳市投资控股有限公司；深圳市怡亚通供应链股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">其他</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">20 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">地方国有资本投资公司；国资并购；国资纾困；战略转型；使命驱动</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Regional state-owned capital investment company; State-owned capital merger and acquisition; State-owned capital bailout; Strategic transformation; Mission-driven</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">深投控作为深圳市国资委下属唯一一家国有资本投资公司，肩负推动地方经济发展和产业升级的使命。2018年，在怡亚通面临财务困境之际，深投控通过并购为其注资纾困，并推动其构建“国企资本+民企管理”新模式。本案例关注地方国有资本投资公司，此类公司一方面以政策导向为特点服务地方经济发展和产业升级，一方面通过市场化资本运作与管理，保持民营企业的市场活力与企业家精神。 本案例旨在引导学员探讨国有资本收购民营上市公司的复杂过程，特别是国资助力民企走出财务困境、实现战略转型的策略和成效，同时理解国资入主民企背后的使命动因。作为典型实践样本，本案例对深化国资功能定位认知和完善民企纾困转型机制具有重要借鉴意义。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Shenzhen Investment Holdings Co., Ltd. (SIHC), as the only state-owned capital investment company under Shenzhen State-owned Assets Supervision and Administration Commission, shoulders the mission of promoting local economic development and industrial upgrading. In 2018, when Eternal Asia faced financial difficulties, SIHC provided relief for the private enterprise through acquisition and promoted the construction of a new model of “state-owned capital + private enterprise management”. This case focuses on regional state-owned capital investment companies, which on one hand fulfill the mission of serving local economic development and industrial upgrading through their policy-oriented characteristics, and on the other hand maintain the market vitality and entrepreneurial spirit of private enterprises through market-oriented capital operations and management. This case aims to guide students in exploring the complex process of state-owned capital acquiring a private listed company, especially the strategies and effectiveness of state-owned capital helping private enterprises overcome difficulties and achieve strategic transformation, while understanding the mission-driven motivations behind state-owned capital&#39;s entry into private enterprises. As a representative practical case, this study provides important insights for deepening understanding of state-owned capital functional positioning and improving private enterprise bailout and transformation mechanisms.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业并购与整合》、《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">国有资本授权经营体制改革；资源依赖理论；协同效应理论；使命驱动理论；并购绩效评估方法</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-08</td>
                            </tr>
